The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: lily, balloon-flower, dahlia, daffodil, begonia, tulip, poppy
The people have 7 different jobs:  bartender, engineer, architect, chef, videographer, pilot, electrician
There are 7 different favourite colors: mauve, ivory, blue, orange, light-blue, emerald, green
