 2. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the bartender##1
 3. the person who likes mauve is the videographer##1
 4. the videographer is on the right of the engineer##1
 5. the person who growspoppy is on the far left##1
 6. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
 7. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 8. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
 9. the person who growsdahlia is on the far right##1
10. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
11. the person playing go is in the middle##1
12. the person playing bridge is on the far left##1
13. the person who growsbegonia is in the middle##1
14. the pilot is on the left of the architect##1
15. the person who likes green is on the left of the person playing poker##1
16. the videographer is on the left of the pilot##1
17. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who likes green##1
18. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the chef##1
19. the person who likes blue is in the middle##1
20. the chef is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
21. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person playing billiard##1

